| footer_align = left
| valign       = middle <!-- style="vertical-align:{{{valign|middle}}};" -->
}}

2010年真人電影《[[惡靈古堡4：陰陽界|惡靈古堡4：陰陽界]]》由男演員[[溫特沃思·米勒|溫特沃思·米勒]]飾演。

2017年，克里斯是CG電影《[[生化危機：血仇殺戮|生化危機：血仇殺戮]]》其中一個主角，其他主角有[[里昂·S·肯尼迪|里昂·S·肯尼迪]]和[[瑞貝卡·錢伯斯|瑞貝卡·錢伯斯]]<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.gematsu.com/2016/03/new-resident-evil-cgi-movie-titled-resident-evil-vendetta#v3A1P3mgLE4za4wQ.99 |title = New Resident Evil CGI movie titled Resident Evil: Vendetta |author = Sal Romano |date = 2016-03-24 |publisher = Gematsu |language = en |accessdate = 2020-10-07 |archive-date = 2020-11-08 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201108124311/https://www.gematsu.com/2016/03/new-resident-evil-cgi-movie-titled-resident-evil-vendetta#v3A1P3mgLE4za4wQ.99 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2021年上映的重啟版電影《[[惡靈古堡首部曲：拉昆市|惡靈古堡首部曲：拉昆市]]》中，由加拿大男演員[[羅比·艾梅爾|羅比·艾梅爾]]飾演克里斯<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://deadline.com/2020/10/resident-evil-reboot-kaya-scodelario-robbie-amell-hannah-john-kamen-origin-story-1234591729/ |title = ‘Resident Evil’ Reboot: Kaya Scodelario, Robbie Amell, Hannah John-Kamen, Neal McDonough & More To Star In Origin Story Adaptation |author = Amanda N'Duka, Anthony D'Alessandro |date = 2020-10-06 |publisher = Deadline |language = en |accessdate = 2020-10-07 |archive-date = 2020-10-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201007143721/https://deadline.com/2020/10/resident-evil-reboot-kaya-scodelario-robbie-amell-hannah-john-kamen-origin-story-1234591729/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

